The '''Fabled Key''' was an ancient [[Sharu/Legends|Sharu]] relic which was used to lock another relic called the [[Mindharp of Sharu/Legends|Mindharp]] in the [[Rafa system/Legends|Rafa system]], sealing away their secrets from a threatening invasion force many millennia ago. Thousands of years later, it was discovered by [[Centran]] governor [[Duttes Mer]] and by a [[Sorcerers of Tund/Legends|Sorcerer of Tund]], [[Rokur Gepta]], both of whom wanted to acquire the [[Mindharp of Sharu/Legends|Mindharp]] and unlock its secrets. Not wanting to risk their own lives, however, and mindful of a local prophecy, they forcibly enlisted the roguish gambler [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] and his [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Vuffi Raa]] to do it for them. After several adventures and misadventures on [[Rafa V]], Lando used the Key to operate the [[Great Lock]] on a Sharu pyramid. Calrissian and his companions were transported inside the pyramid, while the Key sunk into the surface of the lock and became irretrievable.

